column5: Anyone know any info on this seminar?  I usualy reserver getting up early on a day off only for fishing.
I heard it would be Saric,Mania,Pyzer doing a Q&A open mike type deal...
I heard it starts at 8am but I will not be getting out for it if I were only 2 hours closer it would be worth the drive in and head home again hope everyone has a great time.
